  "intent_precise": "BACGene: Using lysis buffer, C+, enzymes (tuberack, slot 6), sample plate (labware, slot 7), lysis_plate (labware, slot lysis plate), PCR plate (labware, slot 8). With temperature module. (1) Wait 0 seconds. (2) Set temperature to 37\u00b0C. (3) Pause for incubation. (4) Transfer from source to destination. (5) Transfer from source to destination. (6) Mix 10 times at 200\u00b5L. (7) Transfer from source to destination. (8) Mix 10 times at 200\u00b5L. (9) Transfer from source to destination. (10) Transfer from source to destination. (11) Transfer from source to destination. (12) Mix 3 times at 50\u00b5L. (13) Transfer from source to destination. (14) Mix 3 times at 18\u00b5L. (15) Incubate for 20 minutes. (16) Set temperature to 95\u00b0C. (17) Incubate for 10 minutes. (18) Set temperature to 37\u00b0C. (19) Transfer from source to destination. (20) Transfer from source to destination. (21) Transfer from source to destination. (22) Transfer from source to destination.",
